commitResults.messageTitle: Rename chatbot from Duke to Carrot
Implement chatbot basic greeting and exit functionality
Reorganise chatbot greeting and goodbye messages into two separate methods
Add functionality to receive userInput and echo
commitResults.messageBody: Level-1 Echo functionality - echos commands entered by the user, and exits when the user types the command bye.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add functionality to store userInput (tasks) and display tasks
commitResults.messageBody: Level-2 Add, List functionality. Add the ability to store whatever text entered by the user and display them back to the user when requested (when user types the keyword "list").

Level-3 Mark/Unmark Tasks.
Add the ability to mark tasks as done (userInput: "mark (taskIndex)"), and not done (userInput: "unmark (taskIndex)").

commitResults.messageTitle: Tweak the code to comply with Java Coding Standard
commitResults.messageBody:
A-CodingStandard.
Changed the code to fit standards as described in https://se-education.org/guides/conventions/java/basic.html

commitResults.messageTitle: Add new nullptr exception block in mark/unmark method
